data.description:
Beautiful freshly painted 5-bedroom home in The Crossings, a quiet and desirable community in southwest Charlotte. Conveniently located near I-485 and I-77 along with many restaurants, great shopping, and Charlotte Premium Outlets just a short distance away. The home sits in a cul-de-sac and has a lot of living space and the owners' suite features a sitting area, huge walk-in closet with lots of storage space, and a garden tub with jets. There is a large flex space off the entrance that can be used as a formal sitting area or an office, along with a formal dining room on the main level. It has a gourmet kitchen with an island featuring a gas top range, separate wall-mounted oven and microwave, breakfast nook, as well as, stainless steel appliances which opens up to the family room with a fireplace, and this makes it a perfect home for entertaining. The Crossings features a pool, cabana area and playground. 
 
Make your appointment today!
